{"tid":1252070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我無諗過自己會開始慢慢步抑鬱失眠 生活失常","createTime":"2019-06-22T20:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T12:34:29.000Z","uid":75156,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2b23b63c0ba0e080fd7bc5a608154b238505e9fe","tid":1252070,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T20:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未到病既<br />\n但徵狀一步步浮現緊"},{"pid":"33a1e6599b69e36f1fcb89c158e7f96c746439cf","tid":1252070,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b23b63c0ba0e080fd7bc5a608154b238505e9fe","tid":1252070,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T20:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未到病既<br />\n但徵狀一步步浮現緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaGVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=6f28e849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！"},{"pid":"0764fb32f299978dfe98d76dd74ab9c25bf5f775","tid":1252070,"uid":36489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:54:10.000Z","msg":"朋友，雖然你無講點解會咁<br />\n但希望你同你朋友傾訴下<br />\n<br />\n再唔係<br />\n<br />\n係度講出嚟，好多朋友會耐心聽你講<br />\n<br />\n你努力了，加油呀"},{"pid":"9a4ff8387570e9c812f670db80170fb391ba92c5","tid":1252070,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0764fb32f299978dfe98d76dd74ab9c25bf5f775","tid":1252070,"uid":36489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:54:10.000Z","msg":"朋友，雖然你無講點解會咁<br /